{"id": 57813, "date": "2025-07-25T04:00:06", "date_gmt": "2025-07-25T11:00:06", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57813"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T12:19:20", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T19:19:20", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-25-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/25/kingdom-of-days-july-25-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 25"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1967:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play at a YMCA pool party at Camp Arrowhead, in Marlboro, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1971:</strong>\u00a0The Bruce Springsteen Band plays an IPO party (really) in Rumson for the Marine International Corporation.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19849\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-07-25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?fit=3237%2C1454&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"3237,1454\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-07-25\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?fit=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?fit=758%2C341&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19849 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?resize=758%2C340&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?w=3237&amp;ssl=1 3237w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?resize=1024%2C460&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?resize=768%2C345&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?resize=1536%2C690&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?resize=2048%2C920&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-07-25.png?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band open for the late, great Dr. John at the Santa Monica Civic Auditorium.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3165\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-0725/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1974-0725.jpg?fit=800%2C624&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"800,624\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-0725\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1974-0725.jpg?fit=300%2C234&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1974-0725.jpg?fit=758%2C591&am